channel.title: I can't wear ammys or capes on hybridscape
channel.description: For some unknown reason when I log into moparscape it's good and all no lag or anything, but when i wear an ammy or a cape the screen freezes then it says error connecting to server attempting to reestablish (kind of like when you lag in runescape) and I go to the moparscape screen and when I try to go in again it says im already logged in... can someone tell me what the problem is?
